  m_text: "Idea: This is a 3D action-roguelike dungeon crawler where players ascend
    the Tower of Sin, battling enemies and bosses (like Greed, Pride and Wrath),
    scaling as the player progresses, until they fail and must start from the beginning
    again. The further you progress in your run before you die, the more you gain
    for your next attempt.\n\nLore: You are a condemned soul. In order to prove you\u2019ve
    been redeemed, you must traverse the Tower of Sin and defeat humanity\u2019s
    fatal flaws: pride, greed, lust, envy, gluttony, wrath, and sloth. Only by climbing
    high enough to reach the end of the tower, can you truly escape."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 331ec03732aaf82448231be7ea651c35, type: 2}
